Mandovi nodik, Goenchea jivitachi jivon rekha oxi pachartat.He nodicho arombh Jamboti zata ani Dudsagorachea toxench Varapoha dhobdhobeantlean pasar zata zoim kaim kodden tika Gomati mhonn vollkhotat jicho arombh ostompt ghanttachea Bhimgad hangasor zata. Mandovi sangata Zuari nodi heo don Goenchea rajeacho mukhel nodi. Goeant, hea nodichi lambai 77 kilometr zavn asa. [[File:Mandovi in Goa 10-26-2008 5-41-46 PM.JPG|thumb|Mandovi nodi]]

Mandovi nodicho proves Goeant Satari talukeant san zata. Hi nodi Kumbharzuvem, Divaddi ani Choddnnem hantuntlean pas zata. Donui Mandovi ani Zuari nodichem udok Orbi doriant lottun ditat ani eka samaneo zagear Cabo Aguada hangasor dhoko rochtat. Ponnji rajdhani ani Pornem Goem-hi adli Goenchi rajdhani donui Mandovichea davea dhodder urtat. Mhapxenchi nodi Mandovichi lhan nhoim zavn asa. 

Kumbharzuvem khariz donui nodink zulloita ani hea khatir Mandovi nodintlean Goenchem mukhel khonniz-lokhnnachem min haddunk-vhorunk sompem zata. Tin motthe goddea udkache zunve Divaddi, Choddnnem ani Vashi, hea nodint Pornea Goeant aspavtat. Choddnnechea sunvear Salim Ali suknnea obhoiavoronn asa jika nanvadik suknnea vinean Salim Ali hanchem nanv dilam, Ek sodanchi feribott hangsorlea ravtoleank hea zunveavoile mukhel zageancher pavovpak adar korta. 

Mandovi nodicho vistar Ponnji, vhoddvikechea Mandovi pula kodden zata. Ho pul 1980 vorsant kosollolo dekhun bodnam zanvk pavla. Novo pul bandun zodd ieradarik hadd- vhor korunk adar korta. Mandovi nodi udexim Ponnji ani Betim ganv zulltat. 

Xinvallea disanim, bharadik bhonvddekaranchea mosamant, khas ratcheo Mandovi nodintlean bottincheo bhonvddeo astat zantunt gavpeanche pongodd Mandovi nodik bhul ghaltat.

